<L>__{exterior shinkai 9000 night}
<A>__{as it continues its descent, it passes corroding metal drums leaking toxic waste, radioactive waste, dumped in the depths, away from prying eyes, and populated areas. the vessel drops into the sulu basin. imagine the grand canyon under forty thousand feet of water. but the sulu basin is ten times the size of the grand canyon. down here, ten thousand fathoms below the storm, all is calm. the dual turbo props on the ear of the submersible kick on. the bathysaphe is now mobile. it glides down the side of an enormous rock face, carefully avoiding massive sandstone pinnacles which jut up from the ocean floor far below.}
